Hi Volks,

I saw a Westfalia camper similar to that one last year at BusFusion. It  
was based on a cube-van version of a baywindow.

There are pictures online here:

http://pottsfamily.ca/VW_type2/BusFusion2002/Batch%201/AGF00013.JPG
http://pottsfamily.ca/VW_type2/BusFusion2002/Batch%201/AGF00014.JPG

The windows, cabinetry and interior trim are just like what you'd find  
in a regular Westfalia.

